thread.title: Jason Huebel

author: Jason Huebel
title: Jason Huebel
text:
TopTal has a truly great talent pool to choose from. But be quick! Companies are snapping up these highly qualified contract employees as quickly as TopTal can recommend them. It took a few tries to find a good fit for our first project, but we've been completely satisfied with our engagements with TopTal. They are professional, highly skilled and deliver results.
Jason Huebel
Director of E-Commerce
Gopher Industrial, Inc.
